gdata.wizard.session.description.message: Please pick an existing session or enter your email address to create a new session. You only need one session per account.

gdata.wizard.session.legacy.message: The Provider for Google Calendar now uses a newer method with better reliability and features. Please go back and use the non-legacy option to proceed. If you are having trouble with that method, please tell the developer about the issue before continuing. You can use the legacy approach temporarily, but it will be removed after the transition.

propertiesdialog.upgradeDescription.message: The Provider for Google Calendar now uses a newer method with better reliability and features. Please upgrade your calendar, as this will be the only option in the future. If you have issues, you can unsubscribe and re-subscribe using the legacy option for the time being. The upgrade will take a moment if you have a large calendar.

propertiesdialog.upgradeDescription.dupl.message: The Provider for Google Calendar now uses a new method with better reliability and features. You are subscribed to this calendar twice, once with the legacy method and once with the new method. This is the legacy subscription. You can unsubscribe from it and keep the new one.

onboarding.donate.amount.description: The rough equivalent of 15 Euros in your language's native currency, rounded up to a round number. This needs to be in the format that works for a the paypal.me link, it will be expanded to e.g. "https://paypal.me/kewisch/15eur"
